source.name: DOE NEPA Documents
source.description: DOE NEPA Documents are available to members of the public, including categorical exclusion determinations, environmental assessments, environmental impact statements, findings of no significant impact, records of decision, mitigation action plans, notices of availability, notices of intent, supplement analyses, and other notices and documents.
